name: Burn Fast || Die Hard // Original
description: Until recently, humans have existed in the debilitating haze of smug contentedness. Confident in their ability to shame individuals into erroneously taking personal accountability for the environmental disasters caused by corrupt conglomerates. 2560x2560.
